{"id":232747404,"title":"Closet和Wardrobe的差別","content":"嗨 文章很有趣 但就我所知 應該不是這樣分辨的哦 \n這邊分享一下我的的理解～\n\ncloset其實大小沒有一定的定義 並不一定像原po文中貼的圖片那麼大XD 那是富有家庭才會有的等級哈哈哈\n\n一般國外家庭房子裡的closet 大概這個大小吧⬇️\n\nhttps://megapx.dcard.tw/v1/images/13ffc7b1-5d23-4d6b-bd34-d59a63f77529/encode/full\n\n所以不出櫃 窩在裡面還是很悶的（欸不是\n\n那closet和wardrobe真要說的話 差別在哪裡呢？\n\n主要差別在於 \ncloset基本上是房子裡內嵌的一個空間 不會把他歸類在傢俱⬇️\n\nhttps://megapx.dcard.tw/v1/images/aa0c3062-f9ae-4ca1-a0c7-1032b822b085/encode/full\n\n而wardrobe則是可移動式的 是傢俱 擺設在房間裡頭 \n像這個樣子⬇️\n\nhttps://megapx.dcard.tw/v1/images/e6eaff40-9658-4feb-8d4a-b6f243d2570d/encode/full\n\n認真來講是這樣分辨啦 當然現在沒有一定了 好像會有人兩個單詞混著用\n\n另外個人建議closet要精準翻譯的話 翻壁櫥是最準確的 若翻試衣間的話 會直覺讓人聯想到fitting room 性質不同\n\n以上\nㄧ點小想法 歡迎交流 ( ﾟ▽ﾟ)/","excerpt":"嗨 文章很有趣 但就我所知 應該不是這樣分辨的哦，這邊分享一下我的的理解～closet其實大小沒有一定的定義 並不一定像原po文中貼的圖片那麼大XD 那是富有家庭才會有的等級哈哈哈，一般國外家庭房子裡","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"ecc6a486-c4ac-4f76-996d-7dda5dcb8518","replyId":232736169,"createdAt":"2019-12-23T17:17:37.892Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-23T17:17:37.892Z","commentCount":10,"likeCount":18,"tags":[],"topics":["英文"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"語言","forumAlias":"language","school":"HRY","department":"andy8417","replyTitle":"#字辨 出櫃？出什麼櫃？","gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":18}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":false,"withVideos":false,"media":[],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"4f1db242-b1e7-4bfd-9521-14058dea32d3","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/13ffc7b1-5d23-4d6b-bd34-d59a63f77529/320.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/13ffc7b1-5d23-4d6b-bd34-d59a63f77529/320.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/13ffc7b1-5d23-4d6b-bd34-d59a63f77529/320.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":[],"createdAt":"2019-12-23T17:1